data.description: The Sellers will miss their friendly welcoming neighbors in the quiet, quaint neighborhood of their 3 bedroom 1 bath cabin as well as all the different birds and wildlife around, but work takes them too far away. Sugarloaf is a small community about 1-2 miles from the busy main street of Big Bear and is perfect. They love the peace and quiet so nice. The nice front patio is perfect for summer BBQ's or an early morning coffee while enjoying the sights and sounds of the mountains. And once entering the cabin you will find a cozy gorgeous fireplace awaiting you which is perfect for cuddling up during the winter months and an open floor plan to fit lots of family members for those summer vacations. Level parking in the front fits 2 vehicles. Just 15 minutes to ski slopes, hiking trails, lake, shopping, the village and everything Big Bear has to offer! Treat yourself to this amazing get away! (It's also being sold furnished.)  To see a video of the inside: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wtOiVIII1VyTcXsThTzPNaxBZgSOtfVX/view?pli=1 (please cut and paste it)
